author: hwright
msg: Change a macro parameter name so that substitution doesn't affect structure
members also.  It is just through a rather fortunate and consistent use of the
macro that we haven't discovered this yet.  But, we shouldn't count on that
behavior, and this change makes the macro suitable for more general use.
* subversion/include/private/fs_util.h
(SVN_FS__ALREADY_EXISTS): Change the name of the path parameter to path_str.
